   XLCloud Overview XLCloud Flexi XLCloud Performa XLCloud Supra      Notes:
 XLCloud Flexi Series utilize Object Storage. Due to encoding and storage requirements, additional overhead is carried, therefore actual storage usage reported by Nextcloud will be 30% to 50% lower than the space consumed. As guidance, each 150GB of file storage reported by Nextcloud, represents approximately 250GB of space on system storage. XLRestore is designed primarily as a diseaster recovery solution. A copy of the server and storage contents are encrypted and sent to an overseas storage service at the end of every day. These backups are kept for 30 days before being destroyed. If the base system has a XLRestore subscription, then all additional storage units consumped will automatically include a XLTRestore subscription. As general guidance, increased memory will improve overall system performance in typical usage scenarios.
